				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Nh%E1%BB%AF-To%E1%BA%A1i/Canh-ch%E1%BB%A9c-th%C3%A1n/poem-kbVuXu0-7mlLSzOfET8_OA">Canh chức thán - 耕織嘆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Nh%E1%BB%AF-To%E1%BA%A1i/author-Ud87XP5NOsHsg-XBLhCs_Q">Triệu Nhữ Toại</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-Thung-L%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-0MPVf1G_1Kh6ZzHTaLZzyA">Đồng Nguyên sứ quân “Thung Lăng hành” - 同元使君舂陵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%C3%A0ng-II/Linh-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-RFcJ19BEewYgdalHt8jgOg">Linh Tuyền tự - 靈泉寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%C3%A0ng-II/author-UztFnsz2pveDcUQVr9DdHg">Trần Hàng (II)</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Phi/M%C3%A3n-giang-h%E1%BB%93ng/poem-mE38G3vrpQNxAPt31aWNtg">Mãn giang hồng - 滿江紅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Phi/author-c3LgePu9281GzRSNKjalQA">Nhạc Phi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Sinh-t%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A0n-nhi-d%C4%A9/poem-NLrtL8QCgNQgkrUCWjvPEA">Sinh tử nhàn nhi dĩ - 生死閑而已</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-025/poem-bkStrU_Y93lIOWns8NCgRg">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 025 - 山居百詠其二十五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%C3%AA-Khang/T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-nh%E1%BA%ADp-qu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-13/poem-q2p7q2Zh9VsAee9FWep-6w">Tặng tú tài nhập quân kỳ 13 - 贈秀才入軍其十三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%C3%AA-Khang/author-ktzrFwfJkeyrhgg3ubmVdQ">Kê Khang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0-th%C3%A1n/poem-6E7FIE6gDHSy2UWGhlL-Jg">Thư thán - 書嘆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca-t%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A3n-ca/poem-11uUzndZ-dhDkhwHVNYZAg">Trường ca tục đoản ca - 長歌破衣襟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-giang-y%E1%BA%BFn-ti%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%B9i-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91oan-c%C3%B4ng-ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-JQWn3-ZAbbZmwcrpYZJUcw">Tương giang yến tiễn Bùi nhị đoan công phó Đạo Châu - 湘江宴餞裴二端公赴道州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
